    "summary": {
      "value": "Learn the Volcano spell."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Requirements:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">you must have mastered the </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Elementalist </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Class.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You learn the ultimate </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Elementalist </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">spell: </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Volcano</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">.</span> </p><table style=\"width:96.2791%\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:15.3584%\"></col><col style=\"width:12.9693%\"></col><col style=\"width:27.3038%\"></col><col style=\"width:44.3686%\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Volcano</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP:</strong> 40</td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target:</strong> Special</td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</td></tr></tbody></table><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You channel the fury of the planet into a powerful wave of fire and magma. Choose one option: one creature you can see suffers <strong>@DMG[10 fire]</strong> damage; </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>OR </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">you choose any number of creatures you can see, and each of them suffers <strong>@DMG[30 fire]</strong> damage. These amounts increase by 5 if you are </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>level 20 or higher</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, or by 10 if you are </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">level <strong>40 or higher</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">. </span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Damage dealt by this spell ignores Resistances and Immunities.</span> </p><p>Add both <strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.spells.Item.BfZqKbr38FBxLtmH]{Volcano (Single Target)} </strong>and <strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.spells.Item.Tp1aelw8OYtmPpQi]{Volcano (Multi Target)}</strong> spells to your character sheet from the <strong>Elementalist</strong> spell list.</p>",
